description: Create your own Professional Solutions. Flexygo allows you to immediatly build incredible Solutions for companies, professionals and individuals. For easy installation visit https://nuget.flexygo.com/
releaseNotes:
New features:  
 New Process Run button text for changing Run process to any other text
 New help items for porperties on the Notice Sentences forms
 New button for creating property help files directly from propertymanager
 New french and spanish translations for all the system elements
 New Frech Language and Notice sentence object for generating Notices and Emails with SQL Sentences
 Build mails and notifications Based on SQLSentences
 New sysNoticeSentence object for creating Mail and Notices based on SQLSentence
 New frech language definition for system objects
 Included New Error log Object for sentinel features
 Cahnged big buttons on mobile devices to standard size buttons
 Added searchobject return field functionallity. Was allways returning object keyfield
 Outbox send mail fix when using attachments (stored procedure was not loading attachments)
 Integration with Ahora Freeware ERP document management. 

Fixes: 
 All notices read button was not working correctly. Stored procedures has been changed
 Translation string generator fixed. was missing out some of the strings
 Placeholder an separator not working correctly. Storeds have been changed
 New spanish translations for mailing and other objects
 Error in sentinel error severity definition values
 error when sending emails setting the smtpserver parameter to nothing
 Module fail when changing tab after filter child list module.
 Nested combo dependencies erases the last child combo value.
title: Flexygo
